If you need good quality, affordable vision care, you need to check out VSP Vision Care. #VSP_Partner Vision care is so important, even if you don’t wear glasses! An eye exam can help detect more than 270 health conditions, and VSP was founded by doctors who believe everyone should have access to quality care at a good value.

Visit vsp.com/enroll to learn more. �

It’s so important to do what you can to support your well-being and health, and I’m happy to pass the info! You’re welcome! @vspvisioncare

#ad #pfizersponsored When I was about 4 years old, my father put a basketball in my hand, and I ran with it all the way up to today. It’s kept me in good physical shape and helps me escape the craziness that is happening in this world, and I have my father to thank for that.
 
Lung health is extremely important, which is why I’m encouraging my Pops to talk to his healthcare provider about pneumococcal pneumonia vaccination. I recently learned it’s a potentially serious bacterial lung disease that can disrupt your life for weeks. In some cases, it could put you in the hospital or even be life threatening. My father has chronic heart disease and is over the age of 65 – both factors that put him at greater risk for the disease.
 
Visit KnowPneumonia.com at the link in my bio to learn about the risk of pneumococcal pneumonia and talk to your doctor or pharmacist about vaccination. @knowpneumonia

After learning about toxic stress and what it can do to my children, I did more digging on the First 5 California website. The informatio I received has been a huge asset when my children experience these traumatic moments. We can’t always prevent what happens but we can be prepared when it does. 

Visit First5California.com to learn more about toxic stress. Link in bio! @first5california

Here are some fun and easy tips I learned on First 5 California’s website to prevent toxic stress with my kids.  There are so many different ways to go about stopping toxic stress before it starts.  These worked out for me! Learn more and find your approach at First5California.com.  Link in Bio! @first5california

First 5 California has taught me not just about toxic stress, but how to cope with my very own mental health as a parent. It’s not easy looking after little humans all the time and we sometimes need an outlet so we can be the best version of ourselves.  Learn more at First5California.com. Link in bio! @first5california
